TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-BUSYSTATUS:FREE
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:TRUE
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Israeli Independence Day. Commemorates the declaration of inde
 pendence of Israel in 1948. Although Yom HaAtzma’ut is normally observed
  on the 5th of Iyyar\, it may be moved earlier or postponed if observance 
 of the holiday (or Yom HaZikaron\, which always precedes it) would conflic
 t with Shabbat\n\nhttps://hebcal.com/h/yom-haatzmaut-2026?us=api&um=icalen
 dar
END:VEVENT
